snippet.title: The Legality of Gore | Better Explaining Amber Alert
snippet.description:
Amber Alert, a mixtape hosted on the Dark Web made with the intent to shock and disturb... Well duh? But because of it's disturbing nature people got to asking... How is it legal? Well it's a damn good question let's talk about that as well as get some clarity on my mindset and thoughts about it in general. 

Spoiler: I did not enjoy Amber Alert.
